{"type": "article", "id": 29775, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30310, "name": "Plankton Station"}, {"id": 30311, "name": "elevele"}, {"id": 30312, "name": "Alessandra Meacci"}, {"id": 30313, "name": "phd3"}, {"id": 30314, "name": "Maria Novozhilova"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718175946b3lLO2GFoM0rgI7f.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>All Around Lamp by Maria Novozhilova</h3><p>米兰和悉尼这两座城市的建筑轮廓在由 <a href=\"http://www.marianovozhilova.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maria Novozhilova</a> 设计的 All Around 灯具中变成了迷人抽象的柔光。几何形的设计使它能够以任意角度摆放，没有传统的顶部和底部限制，把两盏灯拼在一起还能组成一张小边桌，使用起来非常灵活。由细支架支撑的塑料灯罩上刻着两座城市的地标，在黑暗中透过灯光的照射能够营造出独特的气氛，延续人们对于城市的想象。如果你对这盏城市灯感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.marianovozhilova.com/all-around-lamp.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>中的邮箱进行订购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718214017aZGuhvm3LYi4Hqjx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.510000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071821401742dSQ1vRUbrJ95KC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718214017Xg92wfDGj4P0t1ka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607182140170ew2csdouTKq8VYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718214018ZThtSX51dKIafBNH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718214018IeJZtz47Lsv0iBd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Necksound by Necksound Solutions</h3><p>还记得我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28587.html\">骨传导耳机/太阳眼镜</a>吗？今天要介绍的 Necksound 项链式耳机和它使用了相似的科技，专门为喜欢在运动时听音乐的人打造。它内置一个可以调节的吸附系统，通过磁铁能够紧密地贴合在衣服上，而且使用由防水和防尘的材料打造，不用担心大汗淋漓会影响它工作。戴上后你可以同时听到音乐和外界的声音，可以避免在运动时发生意外。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1892029779/necksound-smart-wireless-necklace-wearable-music-d\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 90 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213957tsRzh1B2QDjYSuLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.455752\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607182139575NMD4J0Of7ETBpL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213957ZYF7RVxiheLtOIcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213957JzLh425rvfamupnX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.398529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213957H1YTRDlkJBFxCNL3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.508824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LOCK by Plankton Station</h3><p>第一眼看到这款名为 LOCK 的咖啡桌时，你或许很难想象用来支撑它的扭曲的桌腿实际上是由竹子制成的。这种和木材相比更加环保的材料已经成为不少设计师用来探索更多造型可能时的首选，荷兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.planktonstation.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plankton Station</a> 将竹子切片之后拼接在一起，通过相扣的结构来保证整张桌子的稳定性。为了更好地搭配咖啡桌的概念，部分的竹片被染上了焦糖色，其余则不做颜色处理，层层叠叠的造型就像是拉花一样，富有新意。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/lock-bamboo-coffee-table-plankton-07-15-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1386 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213936PBWmJQuK1MtqAhx5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213936uBktYVKxNLs0Mrne.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213936xrm3WCfg86YZtXoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213938Ov6gCcht1AkTmZRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213938uG8cJAHrdjLaI3PZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680929\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cat bed by elevele</h3><p>如果你刚巧在为喵星人寻找一张能够巧妙地融合进室内环境的小床，elevele 出品的一系列羊毛猫咪床或许是一个不错的选择。这些形状各异的家具在喵星人不使用的时候同样可以当作收纳篮摆在房间里，用来放杂志或者是充电器、钱包等小物都绰绰有余。elevele 希望用这些漂亮的羊毛制品让人们意识到猫咪床不一定会给人带来突兀的感觉，它们也能成为小巧的家饰。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/elevele?section_id=13268353\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 87.44 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213904Yg3DjMhxplNv1adS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.202500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213904BlTSUsINZvCkhnME.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.565000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213914tlUf50qiKVkzMsP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.428750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Slices by Alessandra Meacci</h3><p>墙面书架固然有着不错的收纳功能，但造型往往比较老套。最近 <a href=\"http://www.alemeacci-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessandra Meacci</a> 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.alemeacci-design.com/#!slices/e6gk6\" rel=\"nofollow\">Slices</a> 系列书架则打破了传统的设计，采用了模块式面板的构造让人们可以在两片之间放上书本。远远看去这些立体书架就好像是一条条悬空游弋的鱼，仿佛将墙面改造成了“海底两万里”的舞台。Slices 的绿色版则被命名为“奇幻森林”，是一片绿油油的巨型龟背竹，作为墙饰同样有让人惊艳的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213842nCDg6W4VjGeBJNiu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.963333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213841mB5cZyIkd2Gr6fXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.296667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213841F3V7bZOx8Hqn1W4t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.651667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213841k8De5ydCrPGlSFuj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213841ZVLbwcvP8nyQKC16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.975000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Chip Off The Old Block by phd3</h3><p>新西兰厚切薯片品牌 Chip Off The Old Block 最近委托 <a href=\"http://work.phd3.co.nz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">phd3</a> 重新设计了一套包装：为了强调延续了三代的历史以及对原料的重视，采用了卡通风格的工装造型，并且在正面印上了一排不同年龄的农夫操作拖拉机的图案，带给人一种朴实友好的感觉。薯片的口味则通过不同的“衣着”来区分，直观又富有趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213809m4OxS7vAiNlke5UE.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213810zT5wKchDnoICLaBU.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213810Y14UALTfuV9pZkGR.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213810yxPLh5vHDmks1AZf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213810BN89VxwyivCHcR3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718213810tTvRhlQdS6Ye3xnp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}